Hello Telemachus, son of Odysseus (king of Ithaca)
and Penelope,
I am godess athena and what i am going to tell you is very important.

Odysseus travelled to Bristol to find some friends. 
Your mother,queen Penelope, didnt manage 
her money properly, 
as result she owes money to merchants who threaten her that if they do not give them their money will kill her.Your family is in grave danger.

Go Telemachus, travel quickly to find Odysseus 
and bring him home,his destiny is here,i will guide you but your journey will be challenging.

Will you manage to solve the puzzles that will lead you 
to find Odysseus? 
Or you will fail and your mothers life would be in danger? 

It's a matter of honour, hurry Telemachus, every minute counts.

Explanation: 

Odysseus, after the fall of Troy, he was shouting full of pride for the gods to hear, how smart he was and that with his invention (the trojan horse) the Greeks defeated the Trojans. When Poseidon heard it, he promised him never to reach Ithaca.
<font>Is Located in the city centre,famous god monument, who tried to tackle your fathers journey home.</font>
<font>Tip: may be this god is roman named,instead of greek</font>
Where will Telemachus go to buy new weapons and armour?

Explanation:

In ancient civilizations (Greece,Egypt,Rome,Persia) on the market you could buy everything including weapons.

Telemachus, hurry, we do not have time. 
Your father is a well-known person in the city, and many festivals took place in honour of his victories in the Trojan War, however, lets not forget that Odysseus has a powerful enemy, Poseidon, and his loyalists are across the city. 
With great pleasure they would kill him in order to get Poseidons favour, they have not done it because I stop them.

You need to equip even more, Odysseus' weapons are old, you will need new ones. Go buy new weapons and armour now. I will have my eyes turned on both of you.

Wake up Telemachus; I saw Odysseus, go and look for him into the city centre.

 he is in a popular place where they are playing tragedies. People wait to cheer him before the theatrical performance begins. 
There are many people and you have to be very careful, locals here are very suspicious to the strangers.
 If say that you are Odysseus's son, it is most likely that they will think you crazy, only Odysseus will recognise you. 

Go and talk to your father, tell him that you must leave quickly.

<p class="MsoNormal">Where will Telemachus find Odysseus?<o:p></o:p></p>
<!--EndFragment-->

Finally, Odysseus, we found you. 

Telemachus already knows that we do not have time, Penelope is in danger, your family is in danger, we need fast horses so we can go quickly to the harbour and get out of here. 

Odysseus go with Telemachus and find two very fast horses, do not worry about anything else, we have enough food on board and already Telemachus bought new weapons.

 we need to leave from here as soon as possible.

<p class="MsoNormal">Where do you have your minds? </p><p class="MsoNormal">Now we have the fast horses we wanted. Odysseus, you need to go back and take your old armour, it's the one you had ten years in the Trojan war, and it is already considered invaluable.</p><p class="MsoNormal"> You lend it for the people to admire it but it is still yours and no one will refuse to give it back.</p><p class="MsoNormal"> When you get it go to the ship, we are leaving at once.<o:p></o:p></p>
<!--EndFragment--></div>

Explanation: 

Odysseus lent his armour to the Museum so that he has an extra income and become his name known throughout the city.

<p class="MsoNormal">Now Odysseus is the time to do what I promised you when conquered Troy with the help of the gods.</p><p class="MsoNormal"> I promised that you would never reach Ithaca because I knew how much you wanted to return back after ten years and how much you love it and your family. </p><p class="MsoNormal">Your ego and pride acted as an obstacle when minutes after the sack of Troy stated how smart you are as if you won the Trojans alone. </p><p class="MsoNormal">Do you think you are superior to a god Odysseus? If you were, then you ll be able to understand that in Bristol did not bring your son goddess Athena, but I, transformed as Athena. </p><p class="MsoNormal">I am Poseidon, the god of  sea, and here in my kingdom, the sea, I have you at my mercy, you and your son and no one, god or human can help you.<br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">
